short_summary: Expansion of FCC's Venture Capital Program
description: FCC seeks development of an expanded venture capital program. In support of this, FCC seeks unbiased opinion, supported by research and industry best practices, to recommend and substantiate in areas of organizational structure, program governance and related roles, and FCC's strategic investment thesis, target market and investment channels approach.
